"{\"uid\": \"focusdailynews.com-celebrate-the-summer-olympics-with-award-winning-spirits\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Are you watching the Summer Olympics in Paris?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 46, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 40, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995429789, \"rank\": 4.570725264344281e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Records have been broken, and heroes have emerged as athletes win medals.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have been sitting on our couch watching the competition and celebrating the champions with some award-winning spirits that have brought home the gold.\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aspen Vodka is the liquid embodiment of its environment: natural, elevatedand transcendent.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\", \"score\": 0.9999955895338589, \"rank\": 4.359188359223182e-06, \"text\": \"Aspen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\"}, {\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8209601376331946e-67, \"text\": \"Vodka\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The liquid epitomizes restraint and environmental consciousness, blending tradition with innovation to deliver a luxury vodka that is beloved for its crisp, smooth, pure taste.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aspen Vodka stands as a testament to quality and environmental stewardship.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\", \"score\": 0.9999955895338589, \"rank\": 4.359188359223182e-06, \"text\": \"Aspen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\"}, {\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8209601376331946e-67, \"text\": \"Vodka\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For those who appreciate the finer things, Aspen Vodka is an ode to luxury and a tribute to the pristine beauty of Aspen, Colorado.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\", \"score\": 0.9999955895338589, \"rank\": 4.359188359223182e-06, \"text\": \"Aspen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspen\"}, {\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8209601376331946e-67, \"text\": \"Vodka\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vodka\"}, {\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9813283490062698, \"rank\": 0.01902691318396951, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Aaron Paul, Bryan Cranston and third-generation Mezcalero, Greogrio Velasco, Dos Hombres is a unique blend of the finest Espadin agave, hand-selected from the hillsides of a small village in Oaxaca.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Carter\", \"score\": 0.8799189321125108, \"rank\": 0.12016187682286882, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron_Carter\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryan_Cranston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bryan Cranston\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryan_Cranston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryan_Cranston\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_cruiser_Velasco\", \"score\": 0.9991449824201538, \"rank\": 0.0007352118064048646, \"text\": \"Velasco\", \"types\": [\"Q11446\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_cruiser_Velasco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_cruiser_Velasco\"}, {\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dos_Hombres\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dos Hombres\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dos_Hombres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dos_Hombres\"}, {\"begin\": 952, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"score\": 0.9999999974652383, \"rank\": 2.5346244838147735e-09, \"text\": \"Oaxaca\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mezcal presents an appealing fragrance and a rich taste that engages the palate, ensuring the distinctive smoothness of our brand.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DOUBLE GOLD MEDAL in the San Francisco World Spirits Competition 2023for Ilegal 7 Year A\\u00f1ejo  Ilegal Mezcal, the #1 mezcal in the world, is a beautifully balanced spirit with alegendary history that includes smuggling and weeklong parties in Caf\\u00e9 No S\\u00e9,a clandestine bar and music hub in Antigua, Guatemala.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mezcal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mezcal\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mezcal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mezcal\"}, {\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigua_Guatemala\", \"score\": 0.9999911132239659, \"rank\": 8.381382148169993e-06, \"text\": \"Antigua\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigua_Guatemala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigua_Guatemala\"}, {\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.241319674561513e-14, \"text\": \"Guatemala\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilegal is delicious,approachable, and perfect for drinking neat or in cocktails and is made 'SinPrisa,' without rush or hurry, and using artisanal methods.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilegal's taste profileis a mouthful of sweet agave with a hint of smoke.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Released specially in November 2022, Ilegal's 7 Year A\\u00f1ejo mezcal is produced artisanally in Oaxaca, Mexico (like all Ilegal mezcal).\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"score\": 0.9999999974652383, \"rank\": 2.5346244838147735e-09, \"text\": \"Oaxaca\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\"}, {\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9676